txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Fine skin from the beasts surrounding the haven of Ost Forod. Deliver the items to Parr Chopley at the centre of the fortress.
'This will help us very nicely, thank you.'
'We could use the fur and skin from the beasts nearby. Poachers have been taking more than usual and our stores are running low.'
